project_descr: The project aims to propose statutory changes and implementation framework for an Environmental Code, an enabling legal framework to achieve sustainable development in Cambodia through a series of legal and ecosystem analyses.

outputs.output_descr: Main outputs of the project: 1-overarching principles and objectives for the Environmental Code 2-jurisdictional analyses 3-nationwide integrated ecosystem mapping and 4-initial proposal for statutory changes and implementation framework for the Code
donor_name: UNITED STATES AGENCY FOR INTERNATIONAL DEVELOPMENT (USAID)
